name: SONG- LOTUS DREAM single
description:
This is my first every NFT mint. The song takes influence from various electronic subgenres such as chillwave, lofi, chillhop. It is also inspired by DMT induced  visions of a lotus flower and my time spent in Asia over the past 4 years. 
Proceeds will go towards the raising of my child who is due in the next couple weeks! Hope you enjoy the track <3
